{
  "version": "2.0",
  "description": "gendoc 文件流水線定義 — 此檔案是流水線的唯一順序來源。新增文件類型：(1) 加入本檔案的 steps；(2) 建立 templates/{TYPE}.md + TYPE.gen.md + TYPE.review.md。不需修改任何 skill 檔案。",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "D01-IDEA",
      "type": "IDEA",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/IDEA.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-auto",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D01-IDEA]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D02-BRD",
      "type": "BRD",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/BRD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-auto",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D02-BRD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D03-PRD",
      "type": "PRD",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/PRD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D03-PRD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D04-PDD",
      "type": "PDD",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/PDD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D04-PDD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D05-VDD",
      "type": "VDD",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/VDD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D05-VDD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D06-EDD",
      "type": "EDD",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/EDD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D06-EDD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D07-ARCH",
      "type": "ARCH",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/ARCH.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D07-ARCH]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D07b-UML",
      "type": "UML",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/diagrams/"],
      "output_glob": "docs/diagrams/*.md",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-diagrams",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D07b-UML]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-diagrams skill，生成 9 大 UML 圖 + class-inventory.md。不走標準 gen→review 流程。class-inventory.md 供 D11-test-plan 和 D13-RTM 讀取。"
    },
    {
      "id": "D08-API",
      "type": "API",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/API.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D08-API]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D09-SCHEMA",
      "type": "SCHEMA",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/SCHEMA.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D09-SCHEMA]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D10-FRONTEND",
      "type": "FRONTEND",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/FRONTEND.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D10-FRONTEND]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D10b-AUDIO",
      "type": "AUDIO",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/AUDIO.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type == game",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D10b-AUDIO]",
      "note": "音效設計文件：BGM/SFX/VO 清單、音效觸發邏輯、引擎設定（Cocos/Unity/HTML5 Web Audio）、資產規格、效能預算"
    },
    {
      "id": "D10c-ANIM",
      "type": "ANIM",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/ANIM.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type == game",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D10c-ANIM]",
      "note": "動畫特效設計文件：骨骼動畫/幀動畫/Tween/粒子/Shader、引擎設定（Cocos/Unity/HTML5 PixiJS）、效能預算與 LOD 策略"
    },
    {
      "id": "D11-test-plan",
      "type": "test-plan",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["docs/test-plan.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D11-test-plan]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D12-BDD-server",
      "type": "BDD-server",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["features/"],
      "output_glob": "features/*.feature",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "test(gendoc)[D12-BDD-server]",
      "note": "BDD-server.gen.md 指示生成多個 .feature 檔案；BDD-server.review.md 審查所有 features/*.feature"
    },
    {
      "id": "D12b-BDD-client",
      "type": "BDD-client",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["features/client/"],
      "output_glob": "features/client/*.feature",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "test(gendoc)[D12b-BDD-client]",
      "note": "BDD-client.gen.md 指示生成多個 .feature 檔案；BDD-client.review.md 審查所有 features/client/*.feature"
    },
    {
      "id": "D13-RTM",
      "type": "RTM",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["docs/RTM.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D13-RTM]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D14-runbook",
      "type": "runbook",
      "layer": "運維層",
      "output": ["docs/runbook.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D14-runbook]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D15-LOCAL_DEPLOY",
      "type": "LOCAL_DEPLOY",
      "layer": "運維層",
      "output": ["docs/LOCAL_DEPLOY.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D15-LOCAL_DEPLOY]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D16-ALIGN",
      "type": "ALIGN",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/ALIGN_REPORT.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-align-check",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D16-ALIGN]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-align-check skill，不走標準 gen→review 流程"
    },
    {
      "id": "D17-HTML",
      "type": "HTML",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/pages/"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-html",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D17-HTML]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-html skill，不走標準 gen→review 流程"
    },
    {
      "id": "D18-CONTRACTS",
      "type": "CONTRACTS",
      "layer": "實作層",
      "output": ["docs/openapi.yaml", "docs/contracts/", "infra/", "scaffold/"],
      "output_glob": "docs/contracts/**/*",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-contracts",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "feat(gendoc)[D18-CONTRACTS]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：從生成文件提取機器可讀規格（OpenAPI YAML, JSON Schema, Pact, IaC, Seed Code）。不走標準 gen→review 流程。兩相對照確保 1:1 實作完整性。"
    }
  ]
}
